title: Campaigning in California and New Mexico, Biden aims to ease voter anxieties
dc:creator: Seema Mehta, Erin B. Logan
description: Just days ahead of the midterm elections, President Biden spent Thursday campaigning for Democratic candidates in California and New Mexico.
content:encoded: Just days ahead of the midterm elections, President Biden spent Thursday campaigning for Democratic candidates in California and New Mexico.

media:content.media:description: President Joe Biden stands on stage with Rep. Mike Levin, D-Calif., and his wife Chrissy, after Biden spoke at a campaign rally Thursday, Nov. 3, 2022, in San Diego. (AP Photo/Patrick Semansky)
